name: Agog 12 Iridescent Crystal
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture single diamond crystal with pink hued iridescent video still texture. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
